              "settings": {
                "html": "<div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:24px\"><div style=\"border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.07);background:#fff\">\n  <div style=\"position:relative\">\n    <img src=\"https://galaxy-waterproof.vercel.app/wp-content/themes/galaxy-waterproof/assets/images/case-1.jpg\" style=\"width:100%;height:240px;object-fit:cover;display:block\">\n    <div style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(0,0,0,.55) 0%,rgba(0,0,0,0) 50%);display:flex;align-items:flex-end;padding:16px\">\n      <span style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#fff\">隔熱防水系統</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:18px 20px\">\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:1.75\">葵涌工廠天台加裝高反射隔熱防水系統，有效降低室內溫度，節省冷氣電費，同時解決滲漏問題。</p>\n    <a href=\"https://wa.me/85252225111\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;display:inline-block;margin-top:14px;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;color:#5BBCBC;text-decoration:none\">WhatsApp 查詢 →</a>\n  </div>\n</div><div style=\"border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.07);background:#fff\">\n  <div style=\"position:relative\">\n    <img src=\"https://galaxy-waterproof.vercel.app/wp-content/themes/galaxy-waterproof/assets/images/case-2.jpg\" style=\"width:100%;height:240px;object-fit:cover;display:block\">\n    <div style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(0,0,0,.55) 0%,rgba(0,0,0,0) 50%);display:flex;align-items:flex-end;padding:16px\">\n      <span style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#fff\">灌漿止漏工程</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:18px 20px\">\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:1.75\">觀塘停車場外牆結構性裂縫持續滲水，採用高壓環氧樹脂灌漿，封堵裂縫，永久止漏。</p>\n    <a href=\"https://wa.me/85252225111\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;display:inline-block;margin-top:14px;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;color:#5BBCBC;text-decoration:none\">WhatsApp 查詢 →</a>\n  </div>\n</div><div style=\"border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.07);background:#fff\">\n  <div style=\"position:relative\">\n    <img src=\"https://galaxy-waterproof.vercel.app/wp-content/themes/galaxy-waterproof/assets/images/case-3.jpg\" style=\"width:100%;height:240px;object-fit:cover;display:block\">\n    <div style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(0,0,0,.55) 0%,rgba(0,0,0,0) 50%);display:flex;align-items:flex-end;padding:16px\">\n      <span style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#fff\">露台防水工程</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:18px 20px\">\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:1.75\">大圍露台積水問題，重做防水層並加設去水坡度，徹底解決積水及滲漏問題。</p>\n    <a href=\"https://wa.me/85252225111\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;display:inline-block;margin-top:14px;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;color:#5BBCBC;text-decoration:none\">WhatsApp 查詢 →</a>\n  </div>\n</div><div style=\"border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.07);background:#fff\">\n  <div style=\"position:relative\">\n    <img src=\"https://galaxy-waterproof.vercel.app/wp-content/themes/galaxy-waterproof/assets/images/case-4.jpg\" style=\"width:100%;height:240px;object-fit:cover;display:block\">\n    <div style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(0,0,0,.55) 0%,rgba(0,0,0,0) 50%);display:flex;align-items:flex-end;padding:16px\">\n      <span style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#fff\">廚房地台防水</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:18px 20px\">\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:1.75\">旺角舊樓廚房地台長期潮濕，重做防水膜，加強收口處理，解決鄰居天花滴水問題。</p>\n    <a href=\"https://wa.me/85252225111\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;display:inline-block;margin-top:14px;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:600;color:#5BBCBC;text-decoration:none\">WhatsApp 查詢 →</a>\n  </div>\n</div></div>"
